  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC433">
        <l>peyareñcu kiḷavi peyaroṭu muṭimē.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/211/mode/1up">211</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/212/mode/1up">212</ref>.</p>
<p>iccūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, niṟutta muṟaiyāṉē peyareccattiṟku muṭipukūṟutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p>urai : peyareccam peyarkoṇṭu muṭiyum eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>varalāṟu : 'uṇṇuñ cāttaṉ' 'uṇṭa cāttaṉ' eṉa varum. uṇṇum, uṇṭa eṉpaṉa peyareccam ; maṟṟu itu kūṟavēṇṭiya teṉṉai ?</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC433-Iḷam-cit1">
<l>'nilaṉum poruḷuṅ kālamuṅ karuviyum</l>
<l>viṉaimutaṟ kiḷaviyum viṉaiyum'</l></lg>	<p>(tol. viṉai - 35)</p>
<p>peyarkoṇṭu muṭital kūṟappaṭṭatu piṟaveṉiṉ, ataṟku viṭai, āṇṭu viṉaimutaṟ kiḷaviyum viṉaiyum eṉavē, viṉaiccollum muṭiyum eṉpatu paṭṭatu eṉṟatu. viṉaimutaṟkiḷavi eṉṟakkāl viṉai viṉaimutalum viṉaimutalākalāṉum, iṉi viṉai yeṉṟakkāl viṉaip peyarēyaṉṟi viṉaiccollumākalāṉum ic cūttiram vēṇṭum eṉpatu.		(37)</p>
    </body>
  </text>

